question: (Ask-amaryllis-academy-sms) The bisharp was jogging around the school grounds and noticed an unfamiliar student. She stopped next to them and took a minute to catch her breath. "Are you *huff* new here?" She asked with her hands on her knees as she regained her composure
answer:
“Uhh…Yeah…My mom just dropped me off. I was actually trying to find the dorm rooms. Do you know where they are?”

@ask-amaryllis-academy-sms

title: Teacher Introduction
body:
Name: Mr. Miranda Manuel 

Species: Krokorok 

Courses: Spanish 

Grading Style: Hard ass but reasonable due to not everyone speaking the language correctly or simply not knowing. Will give A’s if effort is put in. 

Personality: A Spanish teacher who has a deadpan demeanor and makes fun of the students who don’t put effort in anything or are just troublemakers. He comes from the Alola region and is usually relaxed and calm. He likes to eat tropical berries in class and is shown to just talk about his life in class. 

Relationships with other teachers: He gets along well with the other teachers but has a crush on the Computer Science teacher and will give her berries to make her notice him. 

Any other fun stuff: He swears in front of the kids in Spanish but since the kids don’t Spanish that well, he gets away from it.

(art and character by @ask-amaryllis-young-peter)
